<div class="row pt-3">
    <h3 class="text-center">Basic Beginnings</h3>
    <p class="text-center">
        Carlos's musical journey began as early as his first words. An innate passion for music pulsed within him, and
        he was eager to express it. Initially, his introduction to the world of music came from the CDs played during
        car rides, which exposed him to a mix of Latin rhythms and classic rock anthems from the 60s through the 80s.
        However, it was the enchanting melodies of musicals that truly ignited his passion. Although Disney soundtracks
        were his early favorites, his musical tastes soon evolved and diversified.
    </p>
    <p>
        At the tender age of four, Carlos's musical journey took a significant step forward when he became a member of
        the Cathedral choir. This experience not only allowed him to develop his vocal abilities but also introduced him
        to the rhythmic world of percussion, which he played during mass services. This marked the beginning of a
        lifelong relationship with music, one that would shape his identity and provide him with countless opportunities
        for expression, growth, and joy.
    </p>
